_sText:
CS:GO version.

bhop_remi

my vivid dream is now a reality~

this short map uses kz/bhop elements. including basic ladderstrafes, weirdjumps and long jumps of up to 264.

intended to be played with the following settings:

  • 100 tickrate.
  • sv_airaccelerate 100.
  • sv_gravity 800.
  • run speed of 250.

easier settings can work too, but the map might end up being boring.

this is my first map.
